        ": سَأَلْتُهُ عَنْ غُسْلِ اَلْأَضْحَى، قَالَ «وَاجِبٌ إِلاَّ بِمِنًى."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1461 - Ibn al-Mughira narrated from al-Qasim ibn al-Walid, who said:\nI asked Imam (as) about the Ghusl (ritual purification bath) of Eid al-Adha.\nImam (as) said: \"It is obligatory except for those in Mina.\""
        ]
